st distros are systemd-first.</li><li>Take advantage of <a href=\"https://itsfoss.com/vs-code-multi-cursor/\">multi-cursor editing in VS Code</a> to simplify repetitive actions.</li></ul><p>Try <a href=\"https://itsfoss.com/sausage/\">Sausage</a>, and enjoy the classic Bookworm game like experience in the terminal.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://itsfoss.com/sausage/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Play With Words in Linux Terminal With With Bookworm Style Game</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Remember the classic Bookworm game? You can have similar fun in the terminal with Sausage.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://itsfoss.com/content/images/icon/android-chrome-192x192-469.png\" alt=\"FOSS Weekly #25.21: Oh My Bash, Ubuntu&apos;s New Terminal, Pixelify Android, Fedora&apos;s Wayland Gamble and More\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">It&apos;s FOSS</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Abhishek Prakash</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://itsfoss.com/content/images/thumbnail/sausage-terminal-game.png\" alt=\"FOSS Weekly #25.21: Oh My Bash, Ubuntu&apos;s New Terminal, Pixelify Android, Fedora&apos;s Wayland Gamble and More\" onerror=\"this.style.display = &apos;none&apos;\"></div></a></figure>
