-bookmark-title\">Ubuntu 25.10 will Have a Brand New Terminal (and Image Viewer)</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Ubuntu 25.10 replaces its default terminal and image viewer with modern apps.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://itsfoss.com/content/images/icon/android-chrome-192x192-466.png\" alt=\"FOSS Weekly #25.21: Oh My Bash, Ubuntu&apos;s New Terminal, Pixelify Android, Fedora&apos;s Wayland Gamble and More\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">It&apos;s FOSS News</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Sourav Rudra</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://itsfoss.com/content/images/thumbnail/ubuntu-25-10-new-terminal-image-viewer.png\" alt=\"FOSS Weekly #25.21: Oh My Bash, Ubuntu&apos;s New Terminal, Pixelify Android, Fedora&apos;s Wayland Gamble and More\" onerror=\"this.style.display = &apos;none&apos;\"></div></a></figure><h2 id=\"%F0%9F%A7%A0-what-we%E2%80%99re-thinking-about\">&#x1F9E0; What We&#x2019;re Thinking About</h2><p>Are we finally entering the Xorg-less era? <a href=\"https://news.itsfoss.com/fedora-43-wayland-only/\">Fedora has taken the bold move to go for Wayland-only</a> desktop offering in the upcoming version 43.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://news.itsfoss.com/fedora-43-wayland-only/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">No More Xorg! Fedora 43 Will Be Wayland-only</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">A bold move by Fedora. Will everyone be onboard?</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://itsfoss.com/content/images/icon/android-chrome-192x192-467.png\" alt=\"FOSS Weekly #25.21: Oh My Bash, Ubuntu&apos;s New Terminal, Pixelify Android, Fedora&apos;s Wayland Gamble and More\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">It&apos;s FOSS News</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Sourav Rudra</span></div>