rakash</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://itsfoss.com/content/images/thumbnail/sausage-terminal-game.png\" alt=\"FOSS Weekly #25.21: Oh My Bash, Ubuntu&apos;s New Terminal, Pixelify Android, Fedora&apos;s Wayland Gamble and More\" onerror=\"this.style.display = &apos;none&apos;\"></div></a></figure>
